  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFitNesseMojo  
    AbstractSetupsMojo  
    RunTestsMojo
    Goal that runs FitNesse tests using fitnesse.junit.TestHelper.
    SetUpMojo
    This Mojo is devoted simply to fetching and unpacking FitNesse into a correct working directory structure, and making sure everything is cleanly setup for running FitNesse.
    ShutdownMojo
    Goal that shuts down FitNesse.
    TearDownMojo
    Cleanup debris after FitNesse runs.
    VerifyMojo
    Goal that provides summary report on FitNesse tests run with 'run-tests' goal.
    WikiMojo
    Goal that launches FitNesse as a wiki server.
